I purchased this product believing on the reviews. Total scam. The product worked perfectly fine after the few days of purchase. After a week later, the Bluetooth connection started to disconnect and the measurements would not carry out. I would only see my total weight from the scale. It is either the app being shit or the company. I bought the scale because I thought I would be able to see my BMI and other measurements besides my weight. If you're looking for a normal scale just for you weight by all means don't purchase this. Look for something cheaper and better. Hope this helps :)
